  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Tolerability of a Single Dose of STX107 in Adults With Fragile X Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of a Single Dose of STX107 in Adults With Fragile X Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
