  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will consist of a Screening period (up to 14 days), a Treatment period, and a
      Follow-Up period. Sixteen subjects will be enrolled into two sequential dose cohorts - 10 or
      30 mg (or matching placebo) across four study centers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
